How to run the following program on local host.

Step 1: Create an .env file with details for phpmyadmin ie

DB_CONNECTION=mysql
DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DATABASE=github
DB_USERNAME= "your username"
DB_PASSWORD= "your password"

Step 2: Once in the folder of your project, run the command: 

php artisan migrate

Step 3: Now your code is ready to run. To run enter this command in your terminal:

php artisan serve


Note: To view the details of a certain repository, click on the number under ID column.

Hope to hear from you soon.
